task.summary:
Add name key to xml config file
name key added to xml configuration file to allow for the referencing of the step name through the integration testing.

Add test data for integration steps
Test data added for multiple points in the ips process.

Modify import to deal with ANSI encoding and fix external import issue
Extra conditions added to the import scripts and casting added to the AM_PM_NIGHT column which bypasses an error being caused due to inconsistent data types going into the traffic_data table.
Removed prints from common functions that were flooding the console. Small tweak to minimums weight (changed 0's to nan)
Add test script for IPS minimums weight integration
